welcome.  I used to get this stuff before I made the cicuits too fancy, 
guess it's K.I.S.S.--Keep It Simple Sally.

Well, I have a PC again, but I loaned out my audio software, and the guy 
never brougt it back. I noticed it acting up, so I backed up the main files 
several days ago, and had the layout of the new board on flash drive.

Frank-S
